This project automates login functionality testing on the Practice Test Automation website using Java + Selenium WebDriver.

It includes:
✅ Valid login test
❌ Invalid login test with error message validation
📸 Screenshot capture on login

📂 Project Structure
automate_basic_web_login_test/
│
├── Login_test.java                  # Valid login test with success validation
├── invalid_login_test_error_message_verification.java  # Invalid login test
├── Screenshot_after_action.java    # Login test + screenshot capture

🧰 Technologies Used
Java
Selenium WebDriver
ChromeDriver
Eclipse IDE
JDK 8+
Maven (optional for future use)

🧪 Test Scenarios
✅ Valid Login Test
Enter correct credentials
Click login
Verify success message: Logged In Successfully

❌ Invalid Login Test
Enter invalid credentials
Click login
Validate error message: "Your username is invalid!" or "Your password is invalid!"

📸 Screenshot After Action
Takes a screenshot after login attempt for evidence or debugging




